Overview
========

.. code:: console

   $ mitmproxy -s /path/to/cowproxy.py

   ⋮

   $ http_proxy=http://localhost:8080/ curl --include http://www.example.org/
   HTTP/1.1 200 OK
   Content-Type: text/plain
   content-length: 63

   ^__^
   (oo)\_______
   (__)\       )\/\
       ||----w |
       ||     ||

Prerequisites
=============

mitmproxy_ ≥ 0.18

Do not use any earlier version.
mitmproxy fails open when the script causes errors.

.. _mitmproxy:
   https://mitmproxy.org/

